{"word":"προσλαμβάνω","slug":"προσλαμβάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προσλαμβάνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λαμβάνω\">λαμβάνω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘obtain to meet a need’, <b>take, partake of,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on food, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><a href='B:510 27:34'>Ac 27:34</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b><a href='B:510 27:33'>27:33</a>, <a href='B:510 27:36'>36</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘take to oneself’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of bringing someone as traveling companion <b>take along <a href='B:510 17:5'>Ac 17:5</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in a gesture for privacy <b>take (aside) <a href='B:470 16:22'>Mt 16:22</a>; <a href='B:480 8:32'>Mk 8:32</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <b><a href='B:510 18:26'>Ac 18:26</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘treat hospitably’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>welcome, receive <a href='B:510 28:2'>Ac 28:2</a>; <a href='B:520 14:1'>Ro 14:1</a>, <a href='B:520 14:3'>3</a>; <a href='B:520 15:7'>15:7</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 17.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προσλαλέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προσλέγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}